{"tid":596331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京罕見三月雪 原來是中共自製「瑞雪」","createTime":"2018-03-17T13:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T03:41:56.000Z","uid":171257,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"62af3f46e072b8a685d4941140f2163ef759f2a3","tid":596331,"uid":171257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T13:55:57.000Z","msg":"北京罕見<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">三月雪</span></strong> 原來是中共自製「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">瑞雪</span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n全國人大今舉行全體會議，將選出國家主席、國家軍委主席，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">習近平</span></strong>勢將連任，不過，北京也在今天出現罕見的三月雪。這場雪引起兩面意見，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有人認為是天有異兆</span></strong>，也有人稱「瑞雪兆豐年」是好的象徵，後來北京氣象部門坦承，今早用機器人工增雪，這場「瑞雪」是人造的。<br />\n<br />\n中國媒體報導指，今早北京外圍的房山、門頭溝等多地出現雨雪，局部地區地面被白雪覆蓋，白茫茫一片。不少微博網友分享雪花紛飛的影片或照片。<br />\n<br />\n「一個冬天不下，現在又下起了雪，北京厲害了！」對於老北京而言，三月中降雪是十分罕見，特別是今年的冬天，北京沒有太多雪。有網友意有所指的留言，說：「下得真是時候！」覺得這場雪下得有點可疑，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒想到真是當局派人製造的</span></strong>。　<br />\n<br />\n北京市氣象局指出，今早昌平區氣象人員，在延壽大黑山進行人工增雪，並展示現場影片。氣象部門指出，今早京城外圍的房山、門頭溝等多地出現雨雪，局部地區地面被白雪覆蓋，白茫茫一片。截至今早9時，全市平均降雪量0.3公釐，其中市區有0.1公釐，市郊的延慶二海坨則錄得2.8公釐。預測今日北京日間大部分地區會出現雨夾雪或小雪。<br />\n<br />\n據傳統說法，瑞雪兆豐年，這時候下雪農作物不會被凍害，雪融下去的水留則會留在土壤，給農作物積蓄很多水，對春耕播種、農作物生長發育都很有利，是豐收之年的象徵。<br />\n<br />\n不少網友在北京氣象局的微博留言，部分留言已經「被河蟹」，留下的評論大多是好話：「瑞雪豐年，國之瑞祥！」「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">瑞雪兆豐年，人民好領袖，民族有希望</span></strong>！」「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">京都瑞雪，天降聖人，中華復興，萬世不朽！</span></strong>」也有網友酸：「原來是假雪。」「給局長連升3級。」「這要是人工的真討厭了。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我還以為有啥冤情呢</span></strong>。」（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2dHBMmq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2dHBMmq.jpg&h=002cc594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ba47G0k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fba47G0k.jpg&h=ed7994d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yczaTKl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyczaTKl.jpg&h=595c3b6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180317/1316544/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180317%2F1316544%2F&d=Yauu6nwW8lo3geADvX2Jgi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=86d947d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180317%2F1316544%2F&h=b95ff100\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180317/1316544/</a>"},{"pid":"7efa2049ef1de72f109a4f72d53bd0ef2bdfd2e7","tid":596331,"uid":27451,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T13:56:59.000Z","msg":"有乜野是真架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b88644f5173a0d55865b0e3a119844596537ec8","tid":596331,"uid":2419,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有乜野是真架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n假野是真的"},{"pid":"449e97fd181ee86d787afd56a8a2ca4bad02d4cf","tid":596331,"uid":33433,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:01:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老味 落雪都做假"},{"pid":"54891e970733a49b990dd1f8938611597c0771c3","tid":596331,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b88644f5173a0d55865b0e3a119844596537ec8","tid":596331,"uid":2419,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有乜野是真架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n假野是真的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:03:38.000Z","msg":"邊個踢爆架? 好危險架咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\"